2014年6月10日，索尼影視娛樂和{{link-en|Marza動畫星球工作室|Marza Animation Planet}}宣佈電影為真人動畫電影<ref name="Jun2014THR">{{cite magazine |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/sonic-hedgehog-movie-works-at-710867 |magazine=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |title='Sonic the Hedgehog' Movie in the Works at Sony |date=June 10, 2014 |last=Siegel |first=Tatiana |accessdate=February 10, 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926185306/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/sonic-hedgehog-movie-works-at-710867 |archive-date=2015-09-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影將由[[尼爾·H·摩里茲|尼爾·H·摩里茲]]的[[Original_Film|Original Film]]製作，與Takeshi Ito和Mie Onishi共同製片，范·羅比克克斯和埃文·薩塞爾編劇<ref name="Jun2014THR" />。

